{"tid":781120,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【集思廣益】聽日點樣部署先好啊屌","createTime":"2018-08-15T15:42:54.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-16T14:39:00.000Z","uid":15229,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca5dea0779293b7fc516eb3372a88d7968257a0","tid":781120,"uid":15229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:42:54.000Z","msg":"外圍跌、美股跌、夜期跌500點<br />\n叫春都無用啦，諗吓聽日點樣部署好過啦屌<br />\n<br />\n我自己好早已經清咗大部分，只留一手正股，預咗聽朝即走（預蝕幾百）<br />\n<br />\n聽日部署：主要會玩恆指熊OR PUT輪，另玩騰熊OR PUT輪<br />\n<br />\n1. 恆指<br />\n勁假時段估計恆指已跌300點+，一開市再殺多浸<br />\n26700嘅牛以上應該會殺哂<br />\n初步預玩兩樣，先買PUT輪，因為預計後市反彈無力會再插（OR等呢幾日反彈後先買）<br />\n之後再買少量極限牛FOR 即市反彈<br />\n<br />\n2/ 老騰<br />\n應該會直落320，基本上已殺唔少牛<br />\n而睇老騰有可能會短線試到300蚊位，但見現價PUT輪、熊都太貴<br />\n即市再入都未必有肉食，值搏率唔高<br />\n所以應該尾市會買少量極限/ CALL輪搏超賣未來幾日會反彈<br />\n<br />\n但無論如何，正股都唔會再入，以上部署都唔會大手買<br />\n當試吓水溫，因為好耐無入市，呢排都係睇市多<br />\n<br />\n拋磚引玉，各位巴打唔知部署？　<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bde699ff9dafbd7dd933a468d19830a70bf53e89","tid":781120,"uid":19527,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"9點30準時IFC天台等"},{"pid":"6181b2bc9abba478909a4b2d0077781b8764b0a4","tid":781120,"uid":15229,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bde699ff9dafbd7dd933a468d19830a70bf53e89","tid":781120,"uid":19527,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:47:58.000Z","msg":"9點30準時IFC天台等"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:55:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留得青山在啦"},{"pid":"e7d7b806989c207a4c33bdbc2d5846c717d0d386","tid":781120,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-15T15:56:40.000Z","msg":"企定定係度，